Introduction

Yume is a Japanese singer under CMG Stars. She is a member of the girl group LOVE ONE and a former member of ViV under EVA Entertainment.

Yume is also known for being a contestant on MNET's survival show Girls Planet 999, in which she was sadly eliminated in episode 5. During her participation on the show, she was a trainee under Biscuit Entertainment.
